                    <td valign="top"><p class="heading1_title">Area Hotels</p>
                      <p>For your convenience, here is a list
                          of hotels located 7 miles or less from UCLA, This information
                          is provided by the <a href="http://www.housing.ucla.edu/" target="_blank">UCLA
                          Housing Office</a>. They do not investigate, endorse
                          or guarantee any of these hotels or motels. The rates
                          quoted do not include the 14% sales tax and rates are
                          subject to change without notice.</p>                      
                              <p> <span class="heading7_routes">UCLA Guest House</span><br>
    330 Charles Young Drive East, Los Angeles, CA 90095<br>
    310-825-2923, 310-825-6108 (fax)<br>
    E-mail: guesthouse@be.ucla.edu<br>
    Website: <a href="http://www.hotels.ucla.edu" target="_blank">www.hotels.ucla.edu</a></p>                      <p>The newly renovated UCLA Guest House is a 61-room hotel
                          located on the UCLA campus. Single or Double $105&#8211;$110
                          (tax exempt). Some rooms w/kitchenette. Available to
                          UCLA parents, alumni, and campus visitors. Morning coffee,
                          tea, newspaper in lobby. Optional Continental breakfast.
                          Cable TV. Guest laundry.</p>                      
                              <p> <span class="heading7_routes">Tiverton House</span><br>
    900 Tiverton Avenue, Los Angeles, CA 90024<br>
    (310) 794-0280</p>                      <p>Located directly across the street from the Medical
                          Center at the corner of Tiverton and LeConte Avenues.</p>                      
                              <p><span class="heading7_routes">Best Western Westwood 
                                Pacific Hotel</span><br>
    11250 Santa Monica Blvd., Los Angeles, CA 90025<br>
    310-478-1400<br>
    310-478-1234 (fax)</p>                      <p> Special UCLA rates $89. 76 rooms, fitness center, jacuzzi,
                          free parking, voice mail. Complimentary continental breakfast.</p>                      
                              <p><span class="heading7_routes">Brentwood Inn</span><br>
    12200 Sunset Boulevard<br>
    Los Angeles, CA 90049<br>
    800-840-3808<br>
    310-943-2744 (fax) <br>
    Website: <a href="http://www.TheBrentwood.com" target="_blank">www.TheBrentwood.com</a></p>                      <p>Nestled along Sunset Boulevard in Brentwood, just 2
                          miles west of UCLA. Private bungalow-style guestrooms
                          boasting exceptionally comfortable beds offering chenille,
                          and woven jacquard comforters with plush pillows, high
                          wood-beam ceilings, and skylight. The Brentwood is smoke
                          and pet free with rates beginning at $139, which includes
                          parking, high-speed internet, complimentary bottled water,
                          continental breakfast, and afternoon cookies with milk. </p>                      
                              <p><span class="heading7_routes">Century Wilshire 
                                Hotel</span><br>
    10776 Wilshire Blvd., Los Angeles, CA 90024<br>
    310-474-4506 or 800-421-7223<br>
    310-474-2535 (fax)<br>
    Website: <a href="http:\\www.centurywilshirehotel.com" target="_blank">www.centurywilshirehotel.com</a></p>                      <p>European boutique hotel. 2004 rates: $99.95 Singles,
                          $119.95 Doubles, $129.95 Junior Suites. Roll-away beds.
                          $15.00 extra. Special weekly and monthly rates. 55 foot
                          swimming pool. Walk to shops &amp; movies, cable TV.
                          Continental breakfast. Free parking. Walk to UCLA. </p>                      
                              <p><span class="heading7_routes">Claremont Hotel</span><br>
    1044 Tiverton Ave., Los Angeles, CA 90024<br>
    310-208-5957 or 800-266-5957<br>
    310-208-2386 (fax)<br>
    Website: <a href="http:\\www.claremonthotel.com" target="_blank">www.claremonthotel.com</a></p>                      <p>Single $49.50; Double $56; Twin $65. Walk to UCLA. First
                          hotel built in Westwood Village. Old fashioned European
                          charm at affordable rates. Complimentary coffee &amp; tea.
                          Direct dial phone, daily maid service, 24 hr. staff.
                          Visa, M/C, Discover and personal checks welcome. Extended
                          stay rates available. </p>                      
                              <p><span class="heading7_routes">Courtyard by Marriott</span><br>
    10320 W. Olympic Blvd.<br>
    Los Angeles, CA 90064<br>
    310-556-2777<br>
    310-772-0805 (fax)</p>                      
                              <p>UCLA rate $109 single and double. Their 135-room hotel
                          is steps from Avenue of the Stars. Balconies, in room
                          coffee, iron/ironing board and other amenities available.</p>                      
                              <p><span class="heading7_routes">Doubletree Hotel 
                                &#8212; Westwood</span><br>
    10740 Wilshire Blvd., Los Angeles, CA 90024<br>
    310-475-8711 or 800-472-8556<br>
    310-475-5220 (fax)<br>
    Website: <a href="http:\\www.doubletreelawestwood.com" target="_blank">www.doubletreelawestwood.com</a></p>                      <p> Ask for UCLA rate. Includes shuttle to campus. Walking
                          distance to Westwood Village. Full service hotel with
                          heated pool, fitness room and 24 hour room service. Virtual
                          tour online.</p>                      
                              <p><span class="heading7_routes">Half Moon Motel</span><br>
    3958 S. Sepulveda Blvd., Culver City, CA 90230<br>
    310-391-5279</p>                      <p>Rates are $41&#8211;$47. Includes voice mail phone,
                          satellite tv, free movies, free parking. City bus in
                          front takes you to UCLA (5 miles), 7 miles from LAX.</p>                      
                              <p> <span class="heading7_routes">Hotel Angeleno</span><br>
                                170 N. Church Lane<br>
                                Los Angeles, CA 90049<br>
                                (310) 476-6411 or 866-ANGELENO<br>
                                (310) 472-1157 (fax)<br>
                                <a href="http://www.hotelangeleno.com/" target="_blank">www.hotelangeleno.com</a></p>
                              <p>Brand new boutique hotel in Los Angeles. Special UCLA Rate. Full service hotel. Complimentary shuttle to UCLA, Getty Museum, Westwood and Brentwood Villages (within 3 mile radius of the hotel). Located 1 mile from UCLA. West Restaurant and Lounge located on the penthouse level featuring panoramic views of LA. Business Center with PC and Mac Computers. Outdoor heated pool and Indoor Fitness Center. Two line phone with voicemail, CD Player, Flat Screen TVs, Complimentary high-speed and wireless internet, Complimentary HBO, refrigerators, hairdryer, coffeemaker and much more.</p>
                              <p> <span class="heading7_routes">Hotel Del Flores</span><br>
    409 N. Crescent Drive, Beverly Hills, CA 90210<br>
    310-274-5115<br>
    310-550-0374 (fax)</p>                      <p>Old fashioned hospitality and value. $85 and up. Share
                          bath: $65 and up. Weekly rates available. Center of Beverly
                          Hills near restaurants and shops, located 2 miles from
                          UCLA. Near local bus lines.</p>                      
                              <p><span class="heading7_routes">Jolly Roger Hotel</span><br>
    2904 Washington Blvd.<br>
    Marina Del Rey, CA 90291<br>
    310-822-2904<br>
    800-822-2904<br>
    Website: <a href="http:\\www.jollyrgr.com" target="_blank">www.jollyrgr.com</a></p>                      <p>Offers rates on extended stays. Minutes from Venice
                          Beach. Amenities include micro/fridge in room at no extra
                          cost, free satellite TV with HBO, free parking and free
                          wireless DSL. Free continental breakfast served daily. </p>                      
                              <p> <span class="heading7_routes">Ocean Park Hotel</span><br>
    2680 32nd Street, Santa Monica, CA 90405<br>
    310-452-1469 <br>
    Website: <a href="http:\\www.oceanparkhotel.com" target="_blank">www.oceanparkhotel.com</a></p>                      <p>Rooms $250 week &amp; up. Nice area of Santa Monica,
                          near coffee shops, restaurants and Trader Joe&#8217;s.
                          Cool ocean breezes and easy access to bus lines. Rooms
                          include maid service, free local calls, free internet
                          access, cable TV, and plenty of parking. Shared bathroom
                          facilities. Best deal in town! </p>                      
                              <p> <span class="heading7_routes">Royal Palace Hotel</span><br>
    1052 Tiverton Ave., Los Angeles, CA 90024<br>
    310-208-6677<br>
    310-824-3732 (fax)<br>
    Website: <a href="http:\\www.royalpalacewestwood.com" target="_blank">www.royalpalacewestwood.com</a></p>                      <p>36 room newly renovated hotel located two blocks from
                          UCLA Medical Center. Singles starting at $89, doubles
                          starting at $99. Suites and rooms with Jacuzzi tubs starting
                          at $125. Free parking. Complimentary deluxe continental
                          breakfast. Special UCLA &amp; extended stay rates. </p>                      
                              <p><span class="heading7_routes">West End Hotel</span><br>
    1538 Sawtelle<br>
    West Los Angeles, CA 90025<br>
    (310) 444-8990<br>
    (310) 479-1823 (fax)</p>                      
                              <p>Room $165 and up for Weekly Rental. Furnished hotel
                          offers private and shared baths, refrigerator, carpets,
                          laundry, phone, Cable TV, maid service. Friendly clean
                          atmosphere, great location, Utilities included. Easy
                          access to bus lines. No pets.<br>
                      </p>                      <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
                  </tr>
